      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties (Ti-6Al-4V ELI) sourced from coupon tensile tests on production-lot material; geometric dimensions from CMM measurements of test articles.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (880 MPa), and ultimate tensile strength (950 MPa) were characterized from tensile coupon tests on the same production lot as the test constructs. Screw and rod geometry was measured by CMM with 5 µm resolution. Variability in material properties propagated through a Monte Carlo analysis (N=500) confirming <4% QoI uncertainty contribution."
