      "acceptanceCriteria": "N=11 constructs from a single production lot; dimensional inspection confirms all constructs within drawing tolerances; coefficient of variation for stiffness <8%.",
      "rationale": "Eleven constructs were assembled from a single production lot of 7.5 mm non-cannulated pedicle screws and UHMWPE test blocks per ASTM F1717. CMM inspection confirmed all critical dimensions within ±0.05 mm of nominal. Inter-specimen stiffness CoV was 5.3%, consistent with expected manufacturing variability."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
