      "rationale": "The ASTM F1717 test fixture was reverse-engineered from dimensional drawings and replicated in the FEA model. Fixture compliance was characterized experimentally and incorporated into the model. Material properties assigned to the FEA model are consistent with coupon test measurements within combined uncertainty bounds."
