    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors were assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed the required level for Medium model risk. One factor (Test conditions) achieved level 2 against a required level of 3 due to evaluation at a single displacement rate; this gap is accepted given the quasi-static loading regime, dual-laboratory testing, and prior literature supporting rate-insensitive behavior of Ti-6Al-4V constructs under these conditions. Validation metric E/uval < 1.96 for all QoIs and constructs. The FEA modeling framework is accepted as credible for the stated COU.",
